Edna Hibbard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edna_Hibbard 0 Edna Louise Hibbard (May 12, 1894 – December 26, 1942) was a stage and motion picture actress from Detroit, Michigan. She had a sharp tongue and was known for her roles in comedy. Edna_Louise_Hibbard ( May_12_,_1894 – December_26_,_1942 ) was a_stage_and_motion_picture_actress from Detroit , Michigan .
